Ubuntu Security Notices

USN-8048-1












USN-8048-1: Linux kernel (OEM) vulnerabilities








Publication date






17 February 2026










Overview






Several security issues were fixed in the Linux kernel.










Releases







 24.04 LTS













 Open side navigation





Packages



 linux-oem-6.17 - Linux kernel for OEM systems





